,"text_ar":"ثم"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"another plant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and some pronounce it"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DiEapN","text_ar":"ضِعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but this is in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHasab","text_ar":"الحَسَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or grounds of pretension to respect &c.], and does not belong to the present art.: (TA:) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaEawaAtN","text_ar":"ضَعَوَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, TA.) [Golius says, on the authority of Meyd, that it also signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reed of which writing-reeds are made."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%B6%D8%B9%D8%A9/","headword_ar":"ضعة","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_21","lexicon_en":"Muḥammad al-Fattinī, Majmaʿ Biḥār al-Anwār fī Gharāʾib al-Tanzīl wa Laṭāʾif al-Akhbār (d. 1578 CE)","lexicon_ar":"مجمع بحار الأنوار للفَتِّنيّ","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=35395#d29101","body_html":"<span class=\"title1\">[ضعة]</span><span> نه: فيه الضعة الذل والهوان والدناءة، وهاؤه عوض من الواو، وقد تكسر ضاده.</span>"}]}}